{code}
http://localhost:8095/openidserver/forgottenpassword!default.action
{code}

There are two screens involved -- see attached screenshots. Both screens state that Crowd will email the user a new password. Instead they should indicate that Crowd will send a reset password link to the user by email. They can then follow that link and set a new password.

